    <p>This chapter explains how you can integrate <ph keyref="product"/> with a content management
      system (CMS), to edit the data stored in the CMS directly in <ph keyref="product"/>. <ph
        product="editor author developer"><ph keyref="product"/> offers support for Documentum CMS
        and Microsoft SharePoint, but other CMSs can use the <xref
          href="../tasks/howto-custom-protocol-plugin.dita#howto-custom-protocol-plugin"
          format="dita">plugin support</xref> for similar integrations</ph>.</p>
